chat.msg: hola, q tal? ready to go?
hello
nice! i am at the starting point, there's a twig leading to a small island with a tiger on it to my left
where to from here, boss?
go left, slight diagonal down
Perfect, now I'm on the island with the tiger. strangely, he seems pretty chill! there are two small islands near me
one is to the south-east with a butterfly on it and the other one is to the south-west with a parrot. which direction, friend?
go towards the parrot, go down between the parrot and elephant, circling the parrot by going back right. then go over the stone bridge.
got it! i went around the parrot, and passed the elephant. now, i crossed the stone bridge and there's a frog on this new island
i also see a crocodile to my left. let's keep the party going! what's next?
go down under the frog. go right past him, then U turn back heading left. and go over the crocodile
right-o! did the loop around the frog, then jogged past the croc
i'm back at the big island with our elephant on it again. what's the next move?
go left over the stone bridge, then go down once you reach the giraffe. then go over the last bridge, through the snake until you reach the treasure
got it! I crossed the bridge, said hi to the giraffe, went down, navigated past the snake and, voila, I've found the treasure! *finished*

chat.msg: hey, estas listo?
si
perfecto. primero, ve hacia el oeste pasando debajo del banco de madera hasta llegar al camino
casi llegas al puesto de flores, pero en lugar de eso, gira completamente a la izquierda y cruza el camino otra vez, regresa hacia el perro blanco. ¿lo tienes?
si
genial. ahora, cruza esa rama que tienes al sur y sigue bajando
vas a notar otro perro blanco al lado del mantel de picnic a cuadros rojos y blancos. ¿ama?
ok
very good, now continue west, I go over the tablecloth until I touch the bowl of berries
You see it?
yes
nice! now, let's continue
do you see a wooden branch in front of you? you need to cross the river again, but this time, go north
ok
once you've crossed, don't touch the green bush but go around it from the right side till you get to the florist's stand
got it?
yes
awesome
now, turn left, pass under the stand and look for a big bridge. do you see people riding a bicycle on it?
yes
great! keep going to the west, just past the bridge
then, you should see two old people sitting on a bench reading newspapers. can you find them?
yes
great, now go south between the old folks and the wooden branch
can you see a green bush at the end of the branch?
yes
superb! now, move east between the branch and the bush

chat.msg: hey there, estas listo?
yes
awesome! i'm at the tent up north
where to next, my friend?
down, pass the dog on the left side, then go right and above the fire. keep going right and slightly down, under the mushrooms, and stop before you get to the blue car.
gotcha! i'm moving south, passing the dog on the left, now going right and above the fire, sliding under the mushrooms and stopping just before the blue car
so, where to next?
go left, then make a turn to go south along the path. pass the telescope on the right, go down between the telescope and the bush. then go west on the path. go north and west to reach the cabin
alrighty then! going left, turning south, passing the telescope on the right, down between the telescope and the bush, west then north and west again to reach the wooden house
*finished*

chat.msg: hola, you ready?
yes
awesome! okay, first, go southwest under the nearest palm tree
after that, take a sharp right, cross the second tree, and then take a hard left towards the south before you reach the third tree. you're doing great pal!
ok
alright! now keep going until you see a cute little brown puppy. go left of the pup, then take a slight left
after that, make a right turn going south. keep up the good work!
ok
perfect! now, just ahead you'll see a big and a small rock
go right smack between them to reach the water. keep it up!
ok
nice one! now get your virtual toes wet and head into the water
see that large red crab? don't worry, it ain't real, just go right heading west along the big rock
ok
awesome going! keep following the water until you reach a medium-sized rock
ok
sweet! now, be a brave soul and head towards that shark, only to make a quick sharp right turn
hold on, there's more fun ahead!
ok
you're doing great! now, back to land we go! between the medium rock and that cool looking  ball, and then head north
let's do this!
ok
ace! now, just veer a smidge to your left and head north-west
you'll be going between a wicked red tent and a big speaker. keep on trucking!
ok
you're rocking it! next, curve around the tent in a gentle arc, like you're dancing around it
fun, right?
ok
awesome! okay, get ready
now head straight south as if you are going to the sea
ok
but stop! just before you reach the water, turn right (west) and walk under the red kayak
doing good!
ok
great! now, turn right (north) and walk alongside the kayak
ok
fantastic! now, see that small green bush? head straight for it! you've made it, buddy!
